        "I've tried to make peace with being ordinary. Not extraordinary, not special, not exceptional — just ordinary, sufficient, here. The peace keeps slipping but I keep returning to it. Ordinary is a harder aspiration than it sounds. The work of staying okay is real and ongoing and some days it takes everything I have.",
